Up the Beanstalk
Tonight, we have a special sleepy adaptation of the classic fairy tale, Jack & the Beanstalk. A story full of wonder and fantasy, with just enough magic to help you drift off into sweet dreams. 😴 
Sound design: crickets. 
Narrator: Thomas Jones
